\title{rigid morphisms of [event structures](jms-00BN)}
\author{jonmsterling}
\date{2023-10-26}
\taxon{definition}

\import{base-macros}
\meta{source}{\citek{staton-winskel-2010}}

\import{jms-00BN}
\import{jms-00BO}

\p{A \em{rigid morphism} of [event structures](jms-00BN) \Mor{f}{E}{E'} is a monotone function on events that preserves finite [configurations](jms-00BO) and is \em{locally injective} in the sense that for any finite [configuration](jms-00BO) #{x\in\FinCfg{E}} and events #{e_1,e_2\in x} such that #{fe_1 = fe_2}, we have #{e_1=e_2}.}
